data.description: Plantation Point part of The Flower's Plantation !!  Beautiful neighborhood and a beautiful home in a cul-de-sac.  3-BR and 2-1/2 BA nestled in a cul-de-sac with a vinyl fenced back yard and sprawling 30 ft. screened porch across the back.  Updates include: new carpet, quartz countertops, light fixtures, and fresh paint.  The eat in kitchen has beautiful oak flooring and cabinetry.  Huge master suite, and enormous muti-use bonus room with storage over the garage. Great schools, approx. 5 miles from a dog park and close to shopping.  Call for your showing today !!
